org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface MasterServer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Application, Documentable, EquinoxApplication
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CustomMasterServer, DefaultMasterServer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomMasterServerImpl, DefaultMasterServerImpl, MasterServerImpl

    public interface MasterServer
extends EquinoxApplication
    A representation of the model object 'Master Server'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Summary Groups
    • Items
    • Markers
    • Ae Server Information Prefix
    • Monitor Pools
    • Event Pools
    • Data Mapper
    • External Event Monitors
    • External Event Filters
    • Averages
    • Moving Averages

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getMasterServer()
